                    <span>Great book! Not quite up to the first book, "Working on the Edge", but great. The author spares the reader all the scientific, high-tech bs of the "Perfect Storm", and gets down and dirty.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Hard to put down!</div>
